&lt;p&gt;In v1, processing 4 elements requires 4 loops, 4 boundary checks, and 4 stride increments. v2 needs only 1 loop, significantly reducing ALU and instruction issue overhead.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="performance-comparison"&gt;Performance Comparison&lt;/h3&gt;
